given yourself to this person?

01:36:32.996 --> 01:36:34.997
ls it true?
Do you see him every night?

01:36:35.165 --> 01:36:38.876
Go ahead, hit me!
ls that why l should tell you,
because you'll hit me?

01:36:39.043 --> 01:36:41.879
