01:52:10.057 --> 01:52:12.642
He loves me, Papa.

01:52:13.060 --> 01:52:15.353
He loves me.

01:52:15.854 --> 01:52:17.855
[♪♪♪]

01:52:21.777 --> 01:52:23.778
[COSETTE SOBBlNG]

01:52:29.660 --> 01:52:31.035
Take her to our old house.

01:52:32.704 --> 01:52:35.915
lt's going to be all right.
l promise you.

01:52:43.882 --> 01:52:45.925
[PEOPLE SHOUTlNG
lNDlSTlNCTLY]

01:52:51.515 --> 01:52:53.516
[EXPLOSlONS lN DlSTANCE]

01:52:56.353 --> 01:52:57.728
[GENDARME SHOUTlNG
lNDlSTlNCTLY]

01:52:59.273 --> 01:53:00.314
